data.text:
Nash Brennan and Jessica Buchanan are fictional characters and a supercouple from the American daytime drama One Life to Live.[1] Nash was portrayed by Forbes March, and Jessica is portrayed by Bree Williamson.[1] They were originally paired together while Jessica's alternate personality, Tess, was in control. The Nash and Tess pairing also gained supercouple status.[2][3]

The couple drew a large fanbase. They were a prominent couple on the series from 2005 to 2008,[1] and were listed as one of fifteen top One Life to Live couples.[4]
